{"tid":425623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"怪大叔巴士耍雜技 狂揼心口除鞋玩拗腰","createTime":"2017-10-06T01:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T09:11:59.000Z","uid":2547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"751213da32b3144632f05aed40c43e1b3b2f5759","tid":425623,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:28:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ItI3rgbEoqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FItI3rgbEoqs&d=JuMPYOSyz7EowLnPmpXzyaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=829b1259\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ItI3rgbEoqs</a><br />\n<br />\n搭公共交通工具耐唔耐都會遇上奇人怪事，facebook有網民就上載片段，見到一個5、60歲嘅中年大叔，喺巴士下層後排「耍雜技」，狂揼自己心口，仲除鞋大玩倒立，認真嚇人。<br />\nfacebook有網民在「Tai Po 大埔」發文，見到九巴72x下層尾排，有一個大叔拗腰屈身，又除鞋上下倒轉，片段更見到大叔連環拳連揼自己心口十幾下，最後「運功」完更要「散功」。<br />\n<br />\n 有網民就留言，話「佢練既武功唔通係江湖失傳好耐既鐵布衫同金鐘罩」，有人覺得大叔似練「神打」，更有網民話「好似鬼上身喎」。亦有網民指，「係東鐵見過佢好多次了」。不過奉勸各位，搭巴士都喺唔好除鞋，更加唔好將腳放喺座位上喇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港真係多痴線佬"},{"pid":"001320735f9c7e61aa7eee4d8d6e27a33377cbd2","tid":425623,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2884104f0b30bf6280626f0d87b90047923414a1","tid":425623,"uid":25099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:32:36.000Z","msg":"拍片條友放返隻仆街腳落地啦, 踩撚住張凳仲衰撚過個呀伯"},{"pid":"e523102f996c18d3da771df05e2779f2ddba59a5","tid":425623,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc697004d5839f5d86802762ca2e07fa31804d1","tid":425623,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:0